title.narrative: Egypt Emergency Labor Intensive Investment Project

description.narrative: The Project Development Objectives are: (i) to create short-term employment opportunities for unemployed unskilled and semi-skilledworkers, and (ii) to provide access to basic infrastructure services to the target population in poor areas in the Borrower's territory.
